These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: zombie, fantasy, romance
3 different pets are kept: horse, lizard, cat
1. the owner of the cat is somewhere between the person watching zombie movies and the owner of the lizard##7
2. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the lizard##5
3. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the lizard##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | fantasy | zombie |
| Pet           | lizard  | cat     | horse  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, r&b, folk
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi, helicopter
1. the person driving the quad-bike is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of funk is somewhere between the fan of folk and the person driving the taxi##7
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | funk | folk |
| Transport     | taxi       | helicopter     | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, tea, almond-milk
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, bike, quad-bike
1. the person driving the bike is somewhere between the person drinking sprite and the person driving the motorbike##7
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |   3    |
| Beverage    | sprite | tea | almond-milk  |
| Transport   | quad-bike  | bike  | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, coach, mechanic
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, epic, superhero
1. the security-guard is somewhere between the person watching superhero movies and the coach##7
2. the person watching epic movies is not the security-guard##6
3. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching epic movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |      3      |
| Job           | coach | security-guard | mechanic     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic    | horror          | superhero |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, jazz, classical
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, car, subway
1. the person driving the car is somewhere between the person driving the subway and the fan of jazz##7
2. the person driving the ship is on the right of the fan of classical##1
3. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | trance      | classical     | jazz   |
| Transport     | subway | car | ship |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-6::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, electronic, soul
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, british, thai
1. the nigerian is on the left or right of the british##3
2. the british is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5
3. the fan of electronic is on the right of the thai##1
4. the fan of electronic is somewhere between the thai and the fan of trance##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | soul    | electronic     | trance     |
| Nationality   | thai | british | nigerian |

