.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-7::.
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, lizard, bird
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, cycling, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere between the owner of the guinea-pig and the person who's sport is volleyball##7
3. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Pet     | bird       | lizard      | guinea-pig       |
| Sport   | volleyball | weightlifting | cycling |

