.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-8::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, police-officer, analyst
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, action, martial-arts
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the chef##3
2. the person watching animation movies is somewhere between the person watching martial-arts movies and the police-officer##7
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the chef##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Job           | analyst | chef  | police-officer |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts      | animation | action      |

