.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, gardening, video-games
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, social-worker, bartender
1. the bartender is not the person who's hobby is video-games##6
2. the social-worker is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the engineer is somewhere between the social-worker and the person who's hobby is gardening##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | gardening | video-games | baking   |
| Job     | bartender    | engineer  | social-worker |

