.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, snowboarding, cycling
1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who's sport is snowboarding##7

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk   | hot-chocolate    | fanta |
| Sport      | cycling | surfing | snowboarding |

