.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-11::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, chess, dancing
There are 3 different nationalities: russian, brazilian, american
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere between the brazilian and the russian##7
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the russian is not the person who's hobby is dancing##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | dancing | cooking | chess |
| Nationality   | brazilian    | american    | russian         |

