.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-12::.
There 3 different types of food: peach, tomato, pineapple
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, sports, time-travel
1. the person watching sports movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching family movies is somewhere between the person watching sports movies and the person eating peach##7
3. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the right of the person watching family movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Food          | peach  | pineapple       | tomato     |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | family | sports |

