.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-13::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, 7up, fanta
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, gospel, trance
1. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the fan of salsa and the fan of trance##7
2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the fan of gospel is somewhere between the fan of salsa and the person drinking 7up##7
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |  3   |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | fanta | 7up |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | gospel    | trance |

