.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-14::.
There 3 different types of food: onion, pear, grapes
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, bus, skateboard
1. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the person eating pear##5
2. the person driving the skateboard is the person eating pear##1
3. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the person driving the skateboard and the person eating onion##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Food        | pear | grapes | onion |
| Transport   | skateboard  | bus       | airplane      |

