2. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere between the owner of the snake and the person who's sport is skiing##7
3. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Pet     | snake  | rabbit       | dog    |
| Sport   | sailing | handball | skiing |

