2. the person eating spinach is the person eating spinach##1
3. the person eating peas is somewhere between the nigerian and the japanese##7
4. the japanese is the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | spinach | peas     | pineapple   |
| Nationality   | nigerian   | egyptian | japanese |

