.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, cola, water
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, social-worker, pilot
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the accountant##1
2. the person drinking water is somewhere between the person drinking cola and the social-worker##7
3. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the social-worker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Beverage   | cola      | water     | milk |
| Job        | pilot | accountant | social-worker    |

 